{"tid":2231401,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張藝興大動作開拓「娛樂集團」　網驚：要離開EXO了？","createTime":"2020-10-05T15:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T04:17:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c36309324cd3a95c1915e17dc0255f7200ee4163","tid":2231401,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"藝人張藝興從南韓天團EXO中出道，有著高大帥氣的長相，且能歌善舞，各方面實力都相當出眾，因此累積了大批歌迷追捧，近年將演藝重心放在大陸，因此時常缺席團體的活動，5日又被發現大動作創了娛樂集團，讓不少網友懷疑難道已經準備離開EXO了，引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5185/d5185378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5185%2Fd5185378.jpg&h=350a38f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張藝興將演藝事業移至大陸。（圖／翻攝自張藝興IG）<br />\n<br />\n張藝興5日在微博上發文，貼出了4張手繪的四神獸Logo，點開圖片後，上面還隱約標記著DNA的字樣，隨即就被翻出，他名下所創立的「染色體娛樂集團」與「核興武器」大動作地開設了各種社群帳號，包含了微博、Instagram、推特等，準備活躍於網路。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5185/5185376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5185%2F5185376.jpg&h=44eda34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張藝興發出疑似集團的Logo。（圖／翻攝自張藝興微博）<br />\n<br />\n然而，張藝興名下娛樂公司開始活動的消息傳出後，也立刻造成熱議，許多歌迷猜測可能與SM娛樂的合約即將到期，也有不少網友擔心他即將離開EXO，甚至有粉絲爆料他與SM娛樂的合約應該在2022年才到期，距離結束還有2年時間，如果要離開公司的話，可能只有打官司一途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5185/5185375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5185%2F5185375.jpg&h=ca62a4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5185/5185377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5185%2F5185377.jpg&h=8847a3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張藝興名下的娛樂集團開設社群帳號。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，張藝興與EXO成員感情還是相當好，他曾在節目《我是唱作人》中，公開曬出自己的桌布，放著與成員們的合照，更開心地透露，每次回到南韓都會與好友們聚會。這一次，張藝興創立娛樂集團，也引起兩派人的討論潮，有部分粉絲表示「期待藝興未來的發展」，也有酸民開嗆「跑跑人再+1」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5185/d5185379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5185%2Fd5185379.jpg&h=f9a03866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張藝興開設娛樂集團，被網友質疑「要離開EXO」。（圖／翻攝自張藝興IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算分隔兩地 EXO既心同EXOL既心都係唔會分開"},{"pid":"a80dfd60073ad272645ae8da631bdb57826a2de3","tid":2231401,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0f284afd0c969c06513fa64292abf142de72c91","tid":2231401,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"G chi 樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21458df62e602ba34a3183160e50b40b3a2b844","tid":2231401,"uid":87394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:38:09.000Z","msg":"受盡唾罵，隻身一人努力賺錢<br />\n為既只係合約到期幫隊友鋪定後路<br />\n兄弟在心中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a3249c28e264fccefd9ee71ca6cb0a8610feb1","tid":2231401,"uid":143093,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"快退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327f6ac8f80fa5cc63512f91ec7eb852b5da6648","tid":2231401,"uid":22210,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"他曾在節目《我是唱作人》中，公開曬出自己的桌布，放著與成員們的合照，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇下有幾虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fae555dbe8ff1a53aa361c1783c562a528b202","tid":2231401,"uid":106533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"佢晨早都同走咗無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7288d33140a7abd7e130a325a18467a8c2b43157","tid":2231401,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2c6088411909b80c68d77e31667af46775f87eb","tid":2231401,"uid":138302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"係就快"},{"pid":"a5363e4fb258d7672a7e76689e1fd7d0cadea924","tid":2231401,"uid":350131,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"支持藝興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b18d6daefe9e0f2ed5d2336b0d72065fa362c17","tid":2231401,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T20:27:31.000Z","msg":"牙哩可否不要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f12d1e7bf7731a496fe54ac915adfcdb62d5ded","tid":2231401,"uid":225464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387118ea1bb907e476f1d51c2a3b2f428ccb7eeb","tid":2231401,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"想睇下咩神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1143a86f150921c566dbf285cad3116fced1259c","tid":2231401,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"第一個形容詞就係高大<br />\n擺明串鳩佢"}]}